doc.title: Derrick

credit.role: Chef der Polizei - der neben dem Polizeipräsidenten sitzt

doc.plot: Stephan Derrick is "Oberinspektor" at the Munich police. Together with his assistant Harry Klein he has to solve murder cases. This series is more based on psychological methods to find out who was the murderer, than on action scenes and car chases. Derrick prefers to talk to people and learn more about their personalities. Therefor the telephone is a very important instrument to him.
